{"name": "graphene-django-graphiql-static", "metadata": {"name": "graphene-django-graphiql-static", "version": "0.6", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django", "Framework :: Django :: 4.2", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: BSD License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3 :: Only", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": "https://github.com/prashantz7242/graphene-django-graphiql-static#readme", "dependencies": [], "summary": "Offline-compatible GraphiQL for Graphene-Django", "upload_time": 1735642651}, "documentation": ["# graphene-django-graphiql-static\n\nGraphene-Django-GraphiQL-Static provides an offline-compatible GraphiQL web UI for Graphene-Django projects. It ensures uninterrupted GraphQL query exploration by serving all necessary assets locally, making it reliable even during internet outages.\n\n## Documentation\n\nThe full documentation is at <https://graphene-django-graphiql-static.readthedocs.io>.\n\n## Quickstart\n\nInstall graphene-django-graphiql-static:\n\n```\npip install graphene-django-graphiql-static\n```\n\nAdd it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:\n\n```python\nINSTALLED_APPS = (\n    # Other installed apps\n    'graphene_django_graphiql_static.apps.GrapheneDjangoGraphiqlStaticConfig',\n)\n```\n\nAdd graphene-django-graphiql-static's URL patterns:\n\n```python\nfrom graphene_django_graphiql_static import urls as graphene_django_graphiql_static_urls\n\n\nurlpatterns = [\n    # Other installed apps\n    url(r'^', include(graphene_django_graphiql_static_urls)),\n]\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- TODO\n\n## Running Tests\n\nDoes the code actually work?\n\n```\nsource <YOURVIRTUALENV>/bin/activate\n(myenv) $ pip install tox\n(myenv) $ tox\n```\n\n## Development commands\n\n```\npip install -r requirements_dev.txt\ninvoke -l\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView", "bases": ["GraphQLView"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.graphiql_template", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.whatwg_fetch_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.react_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.react_dom_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.graphiql_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.graphiql_css_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.subscriptions_transport_ws_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.graphiql_plugin_explorer_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.views.GraphiQLOfflineView.graphiql_plugin_explorer_css_sri", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.admin", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "graphene_django_graphiql_static.__version__", "type": null, "docu